column5: Wow, Went to Gullrock yesterday morn... Unbelievable, that's all I can say...Nice walleyes... 24 inch fatty. a couple of 19 inchers and a whole bunch of saugers. Non stop action for the little time that I was there... Might try East Bay tomorrow.. Lots of little ones but walleye central ... lol... The Family is having prawns and Walleye for Christmas Eve dinner.. mmmmmmmmmerry Christmas MMMMMista W PS: If you want to see the 24 inch walleye you can e-mail me at [email protected]
